@startuml
title Object lifecycle: Gym
[*] --> Cataloged : Codeforces catalog sync sees owned gym
Cataloged --> Assigned : teacher assigns gym to class
Assigned --> StandingSynced : standings sync writes problems and rows
StandingSynced --> StandingSynced : next sync refreshes projection
Assigned --> Unassigned : teacher unassigns gym
Unassigned --> Cataloged : row remains in teacher catalog
Cataloged --> Stale : gym disappears from owned catalog
Stale --> Deleted : stale catalog cleanup removes row
Deleted --> [*]
@enduml
